name: RAK JUNGER #09
description:
When an alien virus infected the world humans and machines bonded. We escaped into the virtual world to fight for our existence. This is new URTH an original series featuring an array of original characters. Rak Junger is a collector of lost souls. He travels the badlands taking the weak and pushes them through the machine to create formidable allies to help fight the war.
